Description: Self-Attention algorithm helper functions and demonstration vignettes of increasing depth on how to construct the Self-Attention algorithm, this is based on Dan Jurafsky and James H. Martin (2022, ISBN:978-0131873216) <https://web.stanford.edu/~jurafsky/slp3/> "Speech and Language Processing (3rd ed.)" and Alex Graves (2020) <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AIiwuClvH6k> "Attention and Memory in Deep Learning".
